    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What is Star Atlas?" class="article-title">
          What is Star Atlas?
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-08T18:23:37Z" title="2025-12-08T18:23:37Z" data-datetime="relative">December 08, 2025 18:23</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47061399229331-What-is-Star-Atlas/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><strong>Star Atlas is a next-generation space exploration game and metaverse powered by blockchain technology and Unreal Engine 5.</strong><br>Set in the year 2620, it invites players to explore a vast, persistent galaxy where they can own, trade, and use digital assets as part of an open economy.</p><p>Whether you're flying ships in 3D space, building fleets, managing resources, or participating in decentralized governance, Star Atlas blends immersive gameplay with Web3 ownership and community collaboration.</p><h3 id="h_01KBJRHZ16E8CV7WMR8XJZD4KQ">Play Across Multiple Experiences</h3><p>Star Atlas isn’t just one game, it’s a growing ecosystem of interconnected gameplay experiences:</p><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/star-atlas-bead34" rel="noopener"><strong>UE5 Game</strong></a><strong> (Epic Games)</strong><br>Fly your ships, explore the galaxy, and engage in multiplayer combat and racing. You can use crew avatars, mine asteroids, and immerse yourself in the future of 3D space gaming</p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://based.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener"><strong>SAGE</strong></a><strong> (Browser-based 4X on-chain game)</strong><br>Explore, craft, and battle with your ships and crew in a fully on-chain strategy game built on Solana</p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://holosim.staratlas.com/"><strong>Holosim</strong></a><strong> (Free-to-Play Browser-based 4X on-chain game)</strong><br>Explore, craft, and battle with your ships and crew in a fully on-chain strategy game built on Atlas net</p></li>
<li>
<a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener"><strong>Fleet Rental</strong></a><br>Create a fleet in SAGE, then list it for rent on <a href="https://play.staratlas.com/rentals/" rel="noopener">Fleet Rental platform</a> so other players can pay to use your ships. Earn passive income without lifting a finger</li>
<li>
<a href="https://play.staratlas.com/market/" rel="noopener"><strong>Galactic Marketplace</strong></a><br>Buy and sell Star Atlas NFTs ships, crew, resources, collectibles and more, using ATLAS or USDC</li>
<li><p><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/fleet/" rel="noopener"><strong>Faction Fleet</strong></a><strong> &amp; </strong><a href="https://play.staratlas.com/claims/" rel="noopener"><strong>Faction Claim</strong></a><br>Stake your ships or Claims Stake for passive rewards like ATLAS and R4 resources</p></li>
<li>
<a href="https://play.staratlas.com/dac/" rel="noopener"><strong>DAC Platform</strong></a><br>Create or join a DAC (Decentralized Autonomous Corporation) directly from the Play site. Collaborate with other players, build your reputation and prepare for future shared governance and gameplay</li>
<li><p><a href="https://govern.staratlas.com/" rel="noopener"><strong>Star Atlas DAO</strong></a><br>Lock POLIS or ATLAS to earn rewards, reduce fees, and vote on proposals that guide the future of the Star Atlas ecosystem</p></li>
</ul><h3 id="h_01KBJRHZ167M2MYW210JFAEVBX">Choose Your Faction</h3><p>At the heart of Star Atlas are three powerful factions vying for control:</p><ul>
<li>
<p><strong>The ONI</strong></p>
<p>A consortium of alien species who, after nearly exterminating one another in war - set aside their differences in the hopes of a more bountiful life in space.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>The Ustur</strong></p>
<p>Spawned by an advanced AI, they are a collective of sentient, soft-formed androids with a developed sense of identity, culture, and fashion.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>The MUD</strong></p>
<p>A faction of humans who were led by a god-like alien being plunder all of the Earth's remaining resources to set off for the promise of the stars.</p>
</li>
</ul><p>Your faction determines your allies, rewards and narrative in the metaverse</p><h3 id="h_01KBJRHZ1614B7VGGB8Q93AS8A">Own and Trade In-Game Assets</h3><p>Every ship, crew member, mining rig, collectible, or resource in Star Atlas is an NFT—stored in your wallet, tradable on the <strong>Star Atlas Marketplace</strong>, and usable in various game modes</p><p>Assets are interoperable across platforms and have direct utility in gameplay, from flying and crafting to staking and upgrading</p></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

